{
  "stem": "5654.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I could see that she had jewelry on her fingers.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my mother-- my sister had told me that my mother had some jewelry and so on.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I said to her, I presume that part of the jewelery that you're wearing, as small as I was, belongs to my parents.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So she got a little bit suspicious about that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she said to me, hang on a minute.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She comes out with a very big frame of my-- my parents' wedding photo.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So always in a frame, it was.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was so pleased about that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- and I said to her, please tell me about what actually happened to my-- how-- how they were caught.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I said to her, I presume you notified the authority there were Jews in these-- into these units.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she didn't like that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But she said to me and my brother, come inside.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we went inside.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she said, that was-- that belonged to your mother.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a sewing machine.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I pulled the drawer open.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And inside, I saw a photograph of my father.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there was a watch, my mother's watch.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So naturally, I took that, the photograph of my father, a tiny little photograph, folded it in half, which I have.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I will show you.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And you see, then I-- I-- it was getting late.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And since I didn't travel on Shabbat, and I decided to-- I wanted to find out.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My uncle lived not very far from where we lived.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I didn't know whether he was alive.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I said to my brother, let's go and-- let's go and see whether Uncle Maurice is alive before we take back the metro to go back into the home.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was getting very close to Shabbat.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
